				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/84/stories-issue-84">Stories</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/nyle-frank">Nyle Frank</a></li><li><a href="/issues/84">November 1982</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


